Discussion.S:
Both anterograde and retrograde studies have shown that 
    neurons in the diagonal band project to the IP (Domesick, '76; 
    Contestabile and Flumerfelt, '81; Hayakawa and Zyo, '82; 
    Hamill and Fass, '84; Hamill and Jacobowitz, '84; the 
    present study).

The present findings largely agree with the results of 
    previous immunohistochemical studies (rat: Ljungdahl et al., 
    "78; Cuello and Kanazawa, '78; Hamill et al., '84; 
    Hemmendinger and Moore, '84; Artymyshyn and Murray, '85; 
    cat: Kapadia and DeLanerolle, '84a,b).
